I agree, but there is hope that catastrophes can be avoided, thanks to some amazing ideas by some

11
00:00:48,879 --> 00:00:54,320
very imaginative scientists. In this programme, we'll be discussing Geoengineering,

12
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:59,759
the name for a collection of new scientific plans to remove carbon from the atmosphere

13
00:00:59,759 --> 00:01:03,600
and stop global warming. Also called climate repair,

14
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:09,200
Geoengineering is still in the experimental stages. Some technologies are controversial because

15
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:14,319
they interfere with natural climate systems, and others may not even be possible.

16
